text: Štefan Olekšák (16 January 1940 - 1 December 1996) was a Slovak skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:1996 deaths Category:Slovak male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Czechoslovakia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:People from Poprad District
